    "content": "<h1 id=\"unstructured-data-for-case-studies\">Unstructured data for case studies<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#unstructured-data-for-case-studies\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h1>\n<p>In addition to the continental structured and comparative data collection exercise. Narrative-based data collection was carried out for the country case studies. The aim of this was to provide country-based analysts with qualitative data that may, or may not, contribute to their own deeper knowledge of their subject matter.</p>\n<p>Data collection was carried out using Perplexity Deep Research following a similar methodology of instructions and metadata. The metadata is recorded in the lower part of the navigation bar.</p>\n<p>Data was collected for:  </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Data exchange  </li>\n<li>Digital identity  </li>\n<li>Digital payments  </li>\n<li>Institutional stakeholders</li>\n<li>Individual stakeholders</li>\n</ul>",
